            </div>
            <div class='w-0.5 h-0 bg-border mt-2'></div>
          </div>
          <div class='flex-1 pb-6'>
            <div class='flex items-center gap-2 mb-2'>
              <span class='font-medium text-foreground'>James Smith</span>
              <span class='text-sm text-muted-foreground'>created new test cases</span>
              <span class='text-xs text-muted-foreground'>1 day ago</span>
            </div>
            <p class='text-sm text-muted-foreground'>Added comprehensive test
              coverage for the new features</p>
            <div class='mt-2 flex gap-2'>
              <span
